metadata.name: Selfportrait
metadata.description:
Selfportrait, 2023

With the anonymity provided by online profile pictures, digital identity has been a widely discussed topic for a long time. Image generation tools add even more layers, allowing us to be whoever we want. How does a selfportrait look like in this parallel world? AI tools are used here to transform the artist's current profile picture into an artwork that includes characteristics of the artist's previous work. This is a selfportrait of the artist's digital identity.
